CEGID seeks a Senior Machine Learning Engineer to join their Artificial Intelligence Center of Expertise (CoE). In this role, you will be responsible for embedding Artificial Intelligence into CEGID's management software products portfolio.

You'll be working within the AI Factory dedicated to advancing CEGID's management software through AI innovation. The primary goal is to seamlessly integrate AI features into the product line, either by enhancing functionality and user experience or by recreating user workflows to take full advantage of AI technology.

What You'll Do


Build and maintain machine learning pipelines to deploy and maintain models in production;
Implement MLOps and LLMOps concepts to streamline the machine learning lifecycle;
Develop and maintain scalable, robust, and efficient machine learning infrastructure;
