What We're Looking For


Bachelor's or Master's in Computer Science, Engineering, or related field;
5+ years in machine learning engineering or software development;
Proficient in Python, with experience in machine learning frameworks like TensorFlow, PyTorch, or Scikit-learn;
Strong expertise in building and maintaining ML models and pipelines;
Strong knowledge of MLOps and LLMOps concepts, with experience in cloud computing platforms, preferably Azure;
Strong communication and collaboration skills.


It Would Be a Plus If You Have


Experience with Azure stack, Generative AI frameworks, Agile or Kanban methodologies, and containerization technologies like Docker and Kubernetes.


